Global Non-woven Glove Machine Market Insights
Non-woven Glove Machine Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Non-woven Glove Machine Market Overview
The Non-woven Glove Machine market has been steadily growing due to the increasing demand for hygiene and safety products across various industries. The global market for non-woven glove machines was valued at approximately USD 1.3 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.8% during the forecast period of 2024-2030. This growth can be attributed to factors such as increased awareness of health and safety standards, rising demand in the healthcare sector, and advancements in machine technology. The market's expansion is also influenced by the growing need for protective gloves in food processing, healthcare, and industrial applications. The Asia-Pacific region remains a dominant player, driven by high manufacturing capabilities and demand from key countries like China and India.

